{
  "stem": "25938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I went to my-- to my neighbor and I heard the-- the-- the-- the radio.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The-- and the radio a voice of Soviet Russia, their representative, that war broke out and Hitler attacked our homeland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time there was no-- there was no transportation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Train didn't run, and there was chaos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the Russians escaped in big trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that about-- we knew about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- I was prepared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew-- I knew-- I knew that it would be a disaster.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people didn't believe me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was-- they said I was a pessimist, they used to call me in my little town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They thought, one of the tragedies of the Jewish people was actually disbelief.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Many people, unfortunately, Jewish people, didn't believe that Hitler would do that, that the Germans would exterminate the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was-- I was one of them who did believe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said-- I said [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's bad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It will be-- it will be a year in destruction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Hitler said in And I read-- I heard his-- his-- his-- speeches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was like a-- like a madman he spoke.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I knew about, I read about-- when Hitler sent out many Jews from Germany to a little camp [POLISH] in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the Jews told-- told the people, the Jewish people, how life in Germany, persecution of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I even wrote a poem at that time about that, but they never published it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I remember when I heard on the radio, I came to my mother, I said, Mom, you had [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm running.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Told her, I have to go to Soviet Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She gave me bread and some, I think, underwear.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
